{"thi-ap38:0.1":"Theriapadana ","thi-ap38:0.2":"Khattiyavagga ","thi-ap38:0.3":"8 Punnikatheriapadana ","thi-ap38:1.1":"“Vipassino bhagavato, ","thi-ap38:1.2":"sikhino vessabhussa ca; ","thi-ap38:1.3":"Kakusandhassa munino, ","thi-ap38:1.4":"konagamanatadino. ","thi-ap38:2.1":"Kassapassa ca buddhassa, ","thi-ap38:2.2":"pabbajitvana sasane; ","thi-ap38:2.3":"Bhikkhuni silasampanna, ","thi-ap38:2.4":"nipaka samvutindriya. ","thi-ap38:3.1":"Bahussuta dhammadhara, ","thi-ap38:3.2":"dhammatthapatipucchika; ","thi-ap38:3.3":"Uggaheta ca dhammanam, ","thi-ap38:3.4":"sota payirupasita. ","thi-ap38:4.1":"Desenti janamajjheham, ","thi-ap38:4.2":"ahosim jinasasane; ","thi-ap38:4.3":"Bahusaccena tenaham, ","thi-ap38:4.4":"pesala atimannisam. ","thi-ap38:5.1":"Pacchime ca bhave dani, ","thi-ap38:5.2":"savatthiyam puruttame; ","thi-ap38:5.3":"Anathapindino gehe, ","thi-ap38:5.4":"jataham kumbhadasiya. ","thi-ap38:6.1":"Gata udakahariyam, ","thi-ap38:6.2":"sotthiyam dijamaddasam; ","thi-ap38:6.3":"Sitattam toyamajjhamhi, ","thi-ap38:6.4":"tam disva idamabravim. ","thi-ap38:7.1":"‘Udahari aham site, ","thi-ap38:7.2":"sada udakamotarim; ","thi-ap38:7.3":"Ayyanam dandabhayabhita, ","thi-ap38:7.4":"vacadosabhayattita. ","thi-ap38:8.1":"Kassa brahmana tvam bhito, ","thi-ap38:8.2":"sada udakamotari; ","thi-ap38:8.3":"Vedhamanehi gattehi, ","thi-ap38:8.4":"sitam vedayase bhusam’. ","thi-ap38:9.1":"‘Jananti vata mam bhoti, ","thi-ap38:9.2":"punnike paripucchasi; ","thi-ap38:9.3":"Karontam kusalam kammam, ","thi-ap38:9.4":"rundhantam katapapakam. ","thi-ap38:10.1":"Yo ce vuddho daharo va, ","thi-ap38:10.2":"papakammam pakubbati; ","thi-ap38:10.3":"Dakabhisincana sopi, ","thi-ap38:10.4":"papakamma pamuccati’. ","thi-ap38:11.1":"Uttarantassa akkhasim, ","thi-ap38:11.2":"dhammatthasamhitam padam; ","thi-ap38:11.3":"Tanca sutva sa samviggo, ","thi-ap38:11.4":"pabbajitvaraha ahu. ","thi-ap38:12.1":"Purenti unakasatam, ","thi-ap38:12.2":"jata dasikule yato; ","thi-ap38:12.3":"Tato punnati namam me, ","thi-ap38:12.4":"bhujissam mam akamsu te. ","thi-ap38:13.1":"Setthim tatonujanetva, ","thi-ap38:13.2":"pabbajim anagariyam; ","thi-ap38:13.3":"Na cireneva kalena, ","thi-ap38:13.4":"arahattamapapunim. ","thi-ap38:14.1":"Iddhisu ca vasi homi, ","thi-ap38:14.2":"dibbaya sotadhatuya; ","thi-ap38:14.3":"Cetopariyananassa, ","thi-ap38:14.4":"vasi homi mahamune. ","thi-ap38:15.1":"Pubbenivasam janami, ","thi-ap38:15.2":"dibbacakkhu visodhitam; ","thi-ap38:15.3":"Sabbasava parikkhina, ","thi-ap38:15.4":"natthi dani punabbhavo. ","thi-ap38:16.1":"Atthadhammaniruttisu, ","thi-ap38:16.2":"patibhane tatheva ca; ","thi-ap38:16.3":"Nanam me vimalam suddham, ","thi-ap38:16.4":"buddhasetthassa vahasa. ","thi-ap38:17.1":"Bhavanaya mahapanna, ","thi-ap38:17.2":"suteneva sutavini; ","thi-ap38:17.3":"Manena nicakulaja, ","thi-ap38:17.4":"na hi kammam vinassati. ","thi-ap38:18.1":"Kilesa jhapita mayham, ","thi-ap38:18.2":"…pe… ","thi-ap38:18.3":"viharami anasava. ","thi-ap38:19.1":"Svagatam vata me asi, ","thi-ap38:19.2":"…pe… ","thi-ap38:19.3":"katam buddhassa sasanam. ","thi-ap38:20.1":"Patisambhida catasso, ","thi-ap38:20.2":"…pe… ","thi-ap38:20.3":"katam buddhassa sasanam”. ","thi-ap38:21.1":"Ittham sudam punnika bhikkhuni ima gathayo abhasitthati. ","thi-ap38:22.1":"Punnikatheriyapadanam atthamam. "}